text: pitabrakd nasa a l laoh banhchea puok anak aoy brakl banhnheu teanglay tow aoy mcheasa robsa ke vinh . haey kalna puok anak kat sechaktei rveang mnoussaalok puok anak trauv katsechakdei daoy you tde thmr . pitabrakd nasa chea kar brasaer bamphot del a l laoh ban phtal dam bau- nmea n dl puok anak . pitabrakd nasa a l laoh mha lyy mha kheunh
